nodes.text: The Shadowlands, designated as Sector 7 by the Galactic Empire, were dark forests on the planet Kashyyyk. During the reign of the Galactic Empire, the Kashyyyk resistance hid in the Shadowlands.
In 14 BBY, Cal Kestis visited the Shadowlands in order to find the Kashyyyk resistance leader Tarfful so he could help Cal on his journey.
